{"title":"怪帽子","authors":["郑秩"],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":8,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"怪帽子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郑秩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自六月十五日天津大公报“大公园地”）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十世纪大时代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事事希奇物物怪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买帽不用君花钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满天乱飞找人戴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写文章戴你一顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多说话戴你一顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要饭吃戴你一顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想民主戴你一顶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帽子样子看不见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帽子厉害似刀剑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是戴上尊脑袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保管老兄跟头栽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是啥子怪帽子？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请君仔细猜一猜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猜到不要大声叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧防帽子由天掉。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}